{
  "stem": "7832.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They-- and they were seeking out Jews on the way to work or on the way home from synagogue, and they were beating them up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were destroying homes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were destroying synagogues.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were pulling out scriptures and burning the Torahs and the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because everybody that went to-- all the men, they-- they-- normally, they leave everything in the temple for the next day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they started to bring everything home, because they were burning synagogues in the areas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So in order to preserve their-- their possessions, they brought them home after each service.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But then they got to it anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they-- and there was a lot of-- a lot of beating up people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one night, I remember, my father had a group of people, and they got together every-- once a week, and they played cards.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they loved to play the violin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they either practiced the violin, and they played cards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there were-- there were about six or eight men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one night, they were playing cards next door, in my-- in our neighbor's house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And where I slept, my window was facing that yard, and I can see that house from my window, from my bedroom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In fact, I went to kindergarten in that house, because one side of the house was made into a-- it was one room, and there was a kindergarten there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, I was woken up by a terrible noise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I got up, and I looked out the window, and I saw a bunch of people were with-- I couldn't make out whether it was-- like, rifles or just big pieces of wood.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were beating somebody up.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
